## 🧠 Core BEA Mathematical Visualization

### The Four Fundamental Operations

```
    E[A] ⊕ E[B] = E[C]     │  COMBUST: 1+1=3 Principle
    ═══════════════════    │  Creates emergent properties
         ╱ ∩ ╲            │  Example: Curiosity ⊕ Bliss = Inspiration
        ╱  ✨  ╲           │
       ╱    ▲    ╲         │
      E[A] ─┼─ E[B]        │
         EMERGENCE         │

    E[A] ⊖ E[B] = E[C]     │  BALANCE: Equilibrium Seeking  
    ═══════════════════    │  Creates stability and harmony
         ╱ ─ ╲            │  Example: Anger ⊖ Passion = Serenity
        ╱  ☯  ╲           │
       ╱    ▼    ╲         │
      E[A] ─┼─ E[B]        │
        HARMONY           │

    E[A] ⊗ E[B] = E[C]     │  DISSOLVE: State Degradation
    ═══════════════════    │  Breaks down complexity
         ╱ ∼ ╲            │  Example: Anxiety ⊗ Calmness = Relief
        ╱  🌧️  ╲           │
       ╱    ▼    ╲         │
      E[A] ─┼─ E[B]        │
      SIMPLIFICATION      │

    E[A] ⊙ E[B] = E[C]     │  AMPLIFY: Enhancement
    ═══════════════════    │  Stabilizing influence from baseline
         ╱ ○ ╲            │  Example: Peace ⊙ Neutral = Curiosity
        ╱  😐  ╲           │
       ╱    ▼    ╲         │
      E[A] ─┼─ E[B]        │
      STABILIZATION       │
```

