## 🎵 Audio Integration Visualization

### Text-to-Speech Emotional Mapping

```
EMOTIONAL AUDIO CHARACTERISTICS:

😐 Neutral     │ ████████████████████████████████ │ Monotone, 120 BPM
🤔 Curiosity   │ ██████████▲▲▲▲████████████████████ │ Rising inflection
😊 Calmness    │ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ │ Soft, flowing
🧐 Interest    │ ████▲████▲████▲████▲████▲████▲█ │ Punctuated
🎉 Excitement  │ ▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲ │ High energy, fast
💪 Strength    │ ████████████████████████████████ │ Strong, confident
✨ Wonder      │ ~~~~~~~~▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲~~~~~~~~▲▲▲▲▲ │ Awe-filled pauses
😄 Joy         │ ♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫♪♫ │ Musical, uplifting
😡 Anger       │ ▲▲▲▲████▲▲▲▲████▲▲▲▲████▲▲▲▲ │ Sharp, staccato
☮️ Peace       │ ________________________________ │ Deep, resonant
```

### Voice Pattern Recognition

```
INPUT AUDIO PROCESSING:

[Microphone] → [FFT Analysis] → [Emotional Classification] → [BEA State]
     │              │                     │                      │
   Audio          Frequency           Pattern                BEABit
   Signal        Components          Matching              Assignment

EMOTIONAL FREQUENCY RANGES:
- Sadness: 80-120 Hz (Low, slow)
- Calmness: 120-180 Hz (Mid-low, steady)
- Excitement: 200-400 Hz (High, variable)
- Anger: 150-300 Hz (Mid, harsh)
- Joy: 180-350 Hz (Mid-high, musical)
```

