## 🔧 BEA Calculator Operations Reference

### Mathematical Operation Details

```
OPERATION: COMBUST (⊕)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Purpose: Creates emergent properties (1+1=3 principle)
Multiplier: 1.5x (COMBUST_MULTIPLIER constant)
Category Enhancement: Transcendent states amplified 2.0x

Example Calculations:
├─ E[1] Curiosity (intensity: 3) ⊕ E[16] Bliss (intensity: 9)
│  → E[27] Inspiration (intensity: 7)
│  Effect: Creative spark emerges from wonder
│
├─ E[7] Joy (intensity: 8) ⊕ E[29] Hope (intensity: 4)
│  → Enhanced Positive State
│  Effect: Optimistic enthusiasm
│
└─ E[19] Clarity (intensity: 5) ⊕ E[6] Wonder (intensity: 7)
   → E[20] Enlightenment (intensity: 10)
   Effect: Transcendent understanding achieved

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

OPERATION: BALANCE (⊖)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Purpose: Seeks equilibrium and harmony
Dampening Factor: 0.8x (BALANCE_DAMPENING constant)
Peaceful States: Enhanced 0.8x weight

Example Calculations:
├─ E[10] Anger (intensity: 7) ⊖ E[23] Passion (intensity: 9)
│  → E[18] Serenity (intensity: 6)
│  Effect: Intense emotions transformed to peace
│
├─ E[4] Excitement (intensity: 6) ⊖ E[2] Calmness (intensity: 2)
│  → E[24] Harmony (intensity: 7)
│  Effect: Energy balanced with tranquility
│
└─ E[13] Anxiety (intensity: 5) ⊖ E[31] Peace (intensity: 8)
   → E[14] Relief (intensity: 3)
   Effect: Tension dissolved into ease

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

OPERATION: DISSOLVE (⊗)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Purpose: Breaks down complex states
Reduction Factor: 0.6x (DISSOLVE_REDUCTION constant)
Simplification: Returns to lower intensity states

Example Calculations:
├─ E[13] Anxiety (intensity: 5) ⊗ E[2] Calmness (intensity: 2)
│  → E[14] Relief (intensity: 3)
│  Effect: Worry breaks down, tension releases
│
├─ E[8] Confusion (intensity: 3) ⊗ E[19] Clarity (intensity: 5)
│  → E[17] Contemplation (intensity: 4)
│  Effect: Uncertainty transforms to reflection
│
└─ E[23] Passion (intensity: 9) ⊗ E[0] Neutral (intensity: 0)
   → E[3] Interest (intensity: 4)
   Effect: Intense drive simplified to focus

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

OPERATION: AMPLIFY (⊙)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Purpose: Returns to baseline, stabilizing influence
Effect: Neutral state centers and grounds emotions
Result: Often produces low-intensity cognitive states

Example Calculations:
├─ E[31] Peace (intensity: 8) ⊙ E[0] Neutral (intensity: 0)
│  → E[1] Curiosity (intensity: 3)
│  Effect: Perfect peace awakens gentle interest
│
├─ E[16] Bliss (intensity: 9) ⊙ E[0] Neutral (intensity: 0)
│  → E[2] Calmness (intensity: 2)
│  Effect: Transcendent joy settles to calm
│
└─ E[10] Anger (intensity: 7) ⊙ E[0] Neutral (intensity: 0)
   → E[0] Neutral (intensity: 0)
   Effect: Intensity completely neutralized

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
```

